What is the Portland Trail Blazers' record?

The Portland Trail Blazers have a record of 13-25.

When is the Portland Trail Blazers' next game?

The Portland Trail Blazers' next game is Tuesday, Jan. 14 vs. BRK.

Where do the Portland Trail Blazers play?

In 2024, the Portland Trail Blazers made 4 picks; Donovan Clingan with the 7th overall pick, Bub Carrington with the 14th overall pick, Tyler Kolek with the 34th overall pick and Osasere Ighodaro with the 40th overall pick.
